Cuddly Doge

As the cats of the dog world, it’s quite rare for a Shiba Inu to roll over for belly rubs, but even more rare to see the famous Doge doing so. Originally captured by her owner Atsuko Sato in February 2010, this image of Kabosu shows a rare side of the beloved meme icon in cuddly fashion before she became the most famous dog to ever grace the web.
